[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":754},["ShallowReactive",2],{"prismic-blog_post-nim-is-on-kucoin":3,"$prismic_navigation":144,"$socialMedias":682},{"id":4,"uid":5,"url":6,"type":7,"href":8,"tags":9,"first_publication_date":10,"last_publication_date":11,"slugs":12,"linked_documents":13,"lang":14,"alternate_languages":15,"data":16},"YlVGUBIAACoAYnk3","nim-is-on-kucoin","/blog/nim-is-on-kucoin","blog_page","https://nimiq.cdn.prismic.io/api/v2/documents/search?ref=aR944RAAACUAypKt&q=%5B%5B%3Ad+%3D+at%28document.id%2C+%22YlVGUBIAACoAYnk3%22%29+%5D%5D",[],"2022-04-12T15:22:40+0000","2023-12-07T16:36:27+0000",[5],[],"en-us",[],{"draft":17,"title":18,"subline":23,"publish_date":28,"authors":29,"image":32,"text":43,"body":47,"meta_title":36,"meta_description":36,"meta_keywords":36,"meta_image":143},false,[19],{"type":20,"text":21,"spans":22},"heading1","NIM is on KuCoin",[],[24],{"type":25,"text":26,"spans":27},"paragraph","Top exchange listing",[],"2019-05-31",[30],{"name":31},"TEAM NIMIQ",{"dimensions":33,"alt":36,"copyright":36,"url":37,"id":38,"edit":39},{"width":34,"height":35},1600,837,null,"https://images.prismic.io/nimiq/9646fcd7-f05f-4e8a-b0ca-a627fcbd309a_blog_+nim-is-on-kucoin_3.png?auto=compress,format","YlVFxBIAACsAYna-",{"x":40,"y":40,"zoom":41,"background":42},0,1,"transparent",[44],{"type":25,"text":45,"spans":46},"",[],[48],{"variation":49,"version":50,"items":51,"primary":53,"id":141,"slice_type":142,"slice_label":36},"default","sktwi1xtmkfgx8626",[52],{},{"backgroundColor":54,"richText":55,"centerHeading":36,"bgColor":54},"grey",[56,58,69,72,76,79,88,92,99,106,114,117,125,133,136],{"type":25,"text":26,"spans":57},[],{"type":25,"text":59,"spans":60},"Nimiq is thrilled to announce that NIM is now listed on KuCoin, one of the most reputable crypto-currency exchanges in the world. The immediate outcome of this integration is the opportunity to educate KuCoin’s extensive user-base about Nimiq, acquire new potential supporters and to further increase the accessibility of the NIM coin for crypto enthusiasts. In addition, of course, the existing Nimiq community also benefits from having another great option to trade NIM.",[61],{"start":62,"end":63,"type":64,"data":65},56,62,"hyperlink",{"link_type":66,"url":67,"target":68},"Web","https://www.kucoin.com/","_blank",{"type":25,"text":70,"spans":71},"You can now buy or sell NIM on KuCoin through the following trading pairs:",[],{"type":73,"text":74,"spans":75},"list-item","NIM/BTC",[],{"type":73,"text":77,"spans":78},"NIM/ETH",[],{"type":80,"url":81,"alt":36,"copyright":36,"dimensions":82,"id":85,"edit":86},"image","https://images.prismic.io/nimiq/78208190-299c-4e0a-855f-f80f93d5d31b_blog_+nim-is-on-kucoin_1.gif?auto=compress,format",{"width":83,"height":84},1024,512,"YlVFxRIAACoAYnbE",{"x":40,"y":40,"zoom":41,"background":87},"#fff",{"type":89,"text":90,"spans":91},"heading2","Tapping into new user-base",[],{"type":25,"text":93,"spans":94},"To raise awareness for NIM’s KuCoin listing and spread Nimiq’s mission to new users, targeted giveaways will be run with the help of our friends at KuCoin. Nimiq has committed a total of 20.5 Million NIM and 250 Nimiq branded Ledgers to these giveaways.",[95],{"start":96,"end":97,"type":98},187,233,"strong",{"type":80,"url":100,"alt":36,"copyright":36,"dimensions":101,"id":104,"edit":105},"https://images.prismic.io/nimiq/e74bad85-de78-4f13-99da-bd70f26d0daa_blog_+nim-is-on-kucoin_2.png?auto=compress,format",{"width":102,"height":103},1200,628,"YlVFxRIAACsAYnbD",{"x":40,"y":40,"zoom":41,"background":42},{"type":25,"text":107,"spans":108},"The conditions of such giveaways will be announced in both KuCoin’s and Nimiq’s social media. If you want to be part of the promotions included with this new listing, then follow Nimiq’s Twitter account and stay tuned!",[109],{"start":110,"end":111,"type":64,"data":112},179,194,{"link_type":66,"url":113,"target":68},"https://twitter.com/nimiq",{"type":25,"text":115,"spans":116},"“KuCoin is extremely proud to announce yet another great project coming to our trading platform.”",[],{"type":25,"text":118,"spans":119},"As part of the listing, KuCoin’s research team has produced their own well researched report on Nimiq.",[120],{"start":121,"end":122,"type":64,"data":123},70,101,{"link_type":66,"url":124,"target":68},"https://blog.kucoin.com/nimiq-nim-token-listing-information-research-project-updates-kucoin",{"type":25,"text":126,"spans":127},"Team Nimiq would like to thank the KuCoin team for their great support in helping us spread the word about Nimiq. Don’t forget to follow our friends at KuCoin on Telegram.",[128],{"start":129,"end":130,"type":64,"data":131},152,171,{"link_type":66,"url":132,"target":68},"https://t.me/Kucoin_Exchange",{"type":25,"text":134,"spans":135},"Pura Vida",[],{"type":25,"text":137,"spans":138},"Team Nimiq",[139],{"start":40,"end":140,"type":98},10,"rich_text$70c0c7b0-43ee-4932-8763-616f99ffb1e1","rich_text",{},{"appsGroupName":145,"appsLinks":146,"howToTitle":301,"appsAdditionalFooterLinks":302,"howToLinks":303,"techGroupName":316,"techLinks":317,"githubLinkLabel":367,"techAdditionalFooterLinks":368,"techItems":369,"communityGroupName":384,"communityLinks":385,"communityItems":418,"communityAdditionalFooterLinks":428,"projectGroupName":431,"projectLinks":432,"projectAdditionalFooterLinks":476,"projectItems":477,"getStartedGroupName":490,"getStartedLinks":491,"newToCryptoTitle":36,"newToCryptoLinks":514,"getStartedAdditionalFooterLinks":515,"andMoreGroupName":516,"andMoreLinks":517,"legalPages":533,"extraHeaderLinks":534,"newsletterCta":535,"newsletterPlaceholder":536,"socialMediaCta":537,"nimiqShortDescription":538,"hothref":539,"hottext":547,"hotsince":548,"hotuntil":36,"announcementBannerHeadline":549,"announcementBannerCtaLabel":550,"announcementBannerCtaLink":551,"announcementBannerShow":17,"blocks":554,"copyrightNotice":681},"Apps",[147,179,197,227,249,275],{"logo":148,"visual":156,"label":165,"href":166,"link":177},{"dimensions":149,"alt":151,"